{"tid":680338,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爸疤有愛　心臟病BB手術捱刀父紋同樣疤痕打氣","createTime":"2018-05-27T06:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T06:40:48.000Z","uid":22739,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"439760a1e0599075a3b0eb085de82af7f96fd480","tid":680338,"uid":22739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:30:09.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】由在媽媽的肚子裏起計，小鐵漢Kansas與爸媽相遇不過兩年，卻已經歷了多次生關死劫。媽媽Doris產檢時發現BB的心臟發育不全，醫生婉轉問「你有冇其他諗法？」「嗰陣都已經五個月，佢可以由咁細粒養到咁大，佢嘅生命力應該好強，所以冇諗過唔要。雖然都知會好辛苦啦。」自此一家三口不停出入醫院。小鐵漢現在已一歲零兩個月，很懂得使計攫取自己想要的，身軀瘦小，與蠱惑的靈魂不太相稱，手術疤痕更顯得粗獷。爸爸Jayco在自己的胸口紋上同樣的圖案，「我個仔條疤痕要孭住一世，我要教佢點面對。如果就咁用口講，佢會話：『你都冇，點知我點諗箒？』我想同佢擁有相同嘅嘢。」<br />\n記者：蔡慧敏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/142834_6b20260c589c25252db55e3132c6e389.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F142834_6b20260c589c25252db55e3132c6e389.png&h=06635d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180527&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20402785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180527%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20402785&d=0gAxxgObGgPCwDOQEb4rKrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=eac5a5f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180527%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20402785&h=618c88b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180527&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20402785</a>"},{"pid":"112ee95380f102cf1ef22cea2aa60ef8e49117cc","tid":680338,"uid":48631,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"死疤狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084119c85812634386a39e09072efbd2ffbd3a74","tid":680338,"uid":22739,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"112ee95380f102cf1ef22cea2aa60ef8e49117cc","tid":680338,"uid":48631,"like":4,"dislike